name: MySQL5
queryCode:
SELECT
    t1.BCODE,
    t1.DEPTID,
    t1.DEPTNAME,
    t1.DOMAINS,
    t1.MEMBERID,
    t1.PERSONNAME,
    t1.POSTID,
    t1.POSTNAME,
    t1.USERID
FROM (
         SELECT
             t11.BUSINESS_CATEGORY as BCODE,
             t31.DEPARTMENT_ID as DEPTID,
             t11.DEPARTMENT_NAME as DEPTNAME,
             t1.DC as DOMAINS,
             t1.ID as MEMBERID,
             t21.DISPLAY_NAME as PERSONNAME,
             t1.ORGANIZATIONAL_ROLE_ID as POSTID,
             t31.NAME as POSTNAME,
             t1.PERSON_ID as USERID
         FROM sys_member t1
                  LEFT JOIN sys_person t21 ON t1.PERSON_ID = t21.ID
                  LEFT JOIN sys_organizational_role t31 ON t1.ORGANIZATIONAL_ROLE_ID = t31.ID
                  LEFT JOIN sys_department t11 ON t31.DEPARTMENT_ID = t11.ID

     ) t1
